name "AWS RDS Backup Settings"
rs_pt_ver 20180301
type "policy"
short_description "![logo](https://s3.amazonaws.com/rs-pft/cat-logos/amazon_rds_glossy.png)

Checks for RDS Instances that have unapproved backup settings. See the [README](https://github.com/rightscale/policy_templates/tree/master/operational/dbaas/aws/rds_backup) and [docs.rightscale.com/policies](http://docs.rightscale.com/policies/) to learn more."
